  <h2>Why Choose Pexotic?</h2>
  <%= image_tag 'exoticpets.jpg' %>
  <ul>
    <li>Lease your exotic pet and earn money</li>
    <li>Rent an exotic pet for a day or more</li>
    <li>Join a community of exotic pet lovers</li>
  </ul>
</div>
